name: 22 Ode to Tezos (Instrumental) - QueenEarth
description:
22 Ode to Tezos (Instrumental) - QueenEarth

Continuing with the release of Introducing QueenEarth 2.0 across the metaverse, this is the first drop on HicetNunc.

Pushed to completion and inspired by Gevik and the Clubhouse NFT community.
Polished by my mix and master genie brother Yacoo. Thank you both for the late nights. 

This instrumental was written during quarantine, for my journey to procreate. I didn't make a baby, yet, but I made a ton of beats and art to get me ready for bigger creating. 

Originally released on Bandcamp, you can hear what good mixing and mastering can do for a track. 

Originally titled "Baby Daddy" https://msqueenearth.bandcamp.com/track/baby-daddy

Remixed for Introducing QueenEarth 2.0 and "Ode to Tezos"
Performed and composed by QueenEarth
Mixed and mastered by El Negro Pacaso
Album artwork by QueenEarth
